snippet.textDisplay:
Excellent... coke studio is very much unique & prolific no matter wherever the studio is situated .. Proud to have it in Bangladesh.. & I can't but have to admire the selection of the song which is very energetic & all the rhythmic presentation of all the musician is very much soothing to ear... 
& the finishing vibe gives the heart a clear message that ,
 " Coke Studio Bangla Has Just Started To Make The Bangla Music Great Again"  ....

snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio's very first song is in "Hajong language" , the language of a small ethnic group .There can't be a more fitting homage in the month of language than this. The Chakma, Garo, Hajong, and Santals are as much a part of Bangladesh as the Bangalis. Coke Studio deserves credit for portraying Bangla music so brilliantly.
